{"tid":1533401,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【急! 召喚post | 831太子】跪求法律、黨鐵同文宣巴絲入","createTime":"2019-09-02T17:11:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T09:07:47.000Z","uid":316638,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"91e6833fe0ccc17c7b5f0d250436bec337bcd3eb","tid":1533401,"uid":316638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:11:04.000Z","msg":"831之後太子封左兩日站，加上兩個鐘頭無記時分，同當時流傳出黎既一啲片段，令大家好懷疑831太子係咪發生咗啲咩。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">首先我要講既係，無論事件中有冇人死亡，831 popo以暴力對待已被制服/對任何人都唔會造成威脅永遠冇可能合理化(無論被制服既人事前有冇做過任何野，呢個都唔係你用法律賦予你武力黎發洩情緒既理由)</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n我睇各位巴絲既發言，歸納咗一啲幫助釐清831既行動，歡迎大家幫手補充!<br />\n(原帖: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1532906/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1532906/page/1</a>)<br />\n<br />\n1. 有冇法律巴絲知道我地可唔可以透過禁制令或者任何法律手段，令黨鐵公開831太子站CCTV片段?<br />\n2. 想問黨鐵巴絲平時邊啲職級可以check到cctv? 同埋831太子站有冇發覺任何異常情況 (例如突然提升左可以睇cctv既職級權限、cctv出現空白片段)?<br />\n3. 會唔會有文宣巴絲幫手推&quot;太子站<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">懷疑</span>死人&quot;，可能local同國際線都要推，逼使黨鐵公開cctv片段。因為依家冇人知當時情況係點，如果講得太肯定確實有機會炒車(我真心想炒車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)，但我地只係想查清真相，我唔想有一絲可能，令任何一位香港人不明不白咁過身。<br />\n<br />\n留比我地既時間唔多，岩岩搵左黨鐵交上立法會附件入邊有CCTV保留期限(<a href=\"https://gia.info.gov.hk/general/201401/22/P201401220275_0275_123767.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgia.info.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2F201401%2F22%2FP201401220275_0275_123767.pdf&d=7ie9SmB3qTQYrTFhvLfIgUwFe44qEnauMGuWilFD6Zg%3D&h=82ff51ae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gia.info.gov.hk/general/201401/22/P201401220275_0275_123767.pdf</a>)，太子站CCTV應該係可以保留28日。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">重申，無論事件中有冇人死亡，831 popo以暴力對待已被制服/對任何人都唔會造成威脅永遠冇可能合理化(無論被制服既人事前有冇做過任何野，呢個都唔係你用法律賦予你武力黎發洩情緒既理由)</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">推呢件事只係覺得好心寒，希望香港仲係我認識既香港。</span></span>"},{"pid":"60828d8d36e770e826478d55f71fd2f044434652","tid":1533401,"uid":55233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:14:06.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d5a17defa9a429d5fdd162103adab08e77c3558c","tid":1533401,"uid":177021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:14:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6a3292b0a6fe04b5b8e895bee03807e2c7dce741","tid":1533401,"uid":316638,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:15:37.000Z","msg":"Push<br />\n不過我知P牌仔推唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e6d2af26b88b421f7d58757f1aa57d7d241df92","tid":1533401,"uid":316788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:26:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fc4354846b372ad6f453957858ef5e46e12d9b3d","tid":1533401,"uid":316638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:35:48.000Z","msg":"推推<br />\n有冇法律巴絲、黨鐵巴絲同文宣巴絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9aa7e0d68e99ae35752c98036a1a9668875b6a2","tid":1533401,"uid":131836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:37:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"baf0ca992d0c2b32408bfeea2064da700cece67d","tid":1533401,"uid":311518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91e6833fe0ccc17c7b5f0d250436bec337bcd3eb","tid":1533401,"uid":316638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:11:04.000Z","msg":"831之後太子封左兩日站，加上兩個鐘頭無記時分，同當時流傳出黎既一啲片段，令大家好懷疑831太子係咪發生咗啲咩。<span style=\"font-size: x-